	<h1 class="title">肢体剧《迷失》又来中国，壁虎剧团的那些执念还是没变</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4369/small/4369.jpg?1419239008" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">晏文静 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-22 19:02:51 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/21166/medium/21166.jpg?1453450115" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="21166" data-title="《肢体剧《迷失》又来中国，壁虎剧团的那些执念还是没变》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/21166/medium/21166.jpg?1453450115" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/21166.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
