<a href="/mobile/articles/12982.html" class="com-grid-key-article">
	<div class="grid-key-article-hd">
		<div class="imgcover">
				<img class="pic" src="/system/articles/banners/12982/medium/12982.jpeg?1438665351" alt="没有谁会因为先锋多买一张票，那孟京辉是如何成了最卖座戏剧导演？">
		</div>
